If you want to use this as a standalone feature without having everyone download the mod do the following

SCRIPT INSTALL

STEP 1:
copy/paste the cau folder and description.ext into your mission file

STEP 2:
modify simplePasswordPrompt.sqf to fit what you want it to do

STEP 3:
add the contents simplePasswordPrompt.sqf into the init field of the device asking for a Password

STEP 4:
add a picture for the BIS_fnc_initInspectable into the mission folder (make sure its a jpg or paa)

STEP 5:
make the players find the PW :)
